This is a cool game - get it.
To play online use "Game Ranger" - theres not many people playing, so encourage your friends to get this game too.

For the NOCD krack - the resulting app is used to REPLACE the actual app after installing. - Just drag  the NOCD app into the game folder & overwrite the installed app.
Otherwise burn a CD using DiscUtility. Mount the DMG (double click it) , then use disc utility to select the DMG & click burn - its that easy.
